				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Breaking Charm....(kind of a n00bish ?)<a name="21698"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Feb 16 04 5:16 PM</span></td>
