				<td colspan="2"><span>can just get the wind mod tribute buff. Or if you get a gazughi ring and people make fun of you coz they have their silly skeeter boots, laugh at them and use this:
<br />

<br />
go to your options, then to your hotkey list. Show ALL hotkeys and change the following to all be bound ot the same easy to reach key:
<br />

<br />
hotbutton 10
<br />
toggle last two targets
<br />
target self
<br />

<br />

<br />
Make sure if ou use (for example) the &quot;U&quot; key that you use the ALTERNATIVE column for all 3 macros. Also the above example assumes you have your gazughi ring hotkeyd to slot 10, when you could also use any other dslot on your hotkey bank and just change the number you bind your key to.
<br />

<br />
what the abovemacro does is target you, click your ring and then retarget your last targetted mob.. it does it all instantly (you dont even see it target yourself). Just make sure you reclick your pet befor you break.</span></td>
